{"id":"api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions","title":"AnimationQueryOptions","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/animations\", \"name\": \"@angular/animations\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions\", \"name\": \"AnimationQueryOptions\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/animations\">@angular/animations</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts?message=docs(animations)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L577-L607\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L577-L607\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"animationqueryoptions\">AnimationQueryOptions<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions#animationqueryoptions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">封裝一些動畫查詢選項。\n傳給 <code><a href=\"api/animations/query\" class=\"code-anchor\">query</a>()</code> 函式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Encapsulates animation query options.\nPassed to the <code><a href=\"api/animations/query\" class=\"code-anchor\">query</a>()</code> function.</p>\n\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationQueryOptions</a> extends <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/animations/AnimationOptions\">AnimationOptions</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions#optional\"><span class=\"member-name\">optional</span>?: boolean</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions#limit\"><span class=\"member-name\">limit</span>?: number</a>\n\n  // 繼承自 <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/animations/AnimationOptions\">animations/AnimationOptions</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/animations/AnimationOptions#delay\"><span class=\"member-name\">delay</span>?: number | string</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/animations/AnimationOptions#params\"><span class=\"member-name\">params</span>?: {...}</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>屬性</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"optional\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">optional</span>?: boolean</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">如果該查詢是可選的，則為 <code>true</code>，如果必選則為 <code>false</code>。預設為 <code>false</code>。\n當執行該查詢時，如果沒有取到元素，則必選查詢會丟擲錯誤，而可選查詢則不會。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">True if this query is optional, false if it is required. Default is false.\nA required query throws an error if no elements are retrieved when\nthe query is executed. An optional query does not.</p>\n\n</div>\n          \n          </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"limit\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">limit</span>?: number</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">從查詢中返回的結果數上限。\n如果為負值，則從查詢列表的末尾往前進行擷取，直到上限。\n預設情況下，結果無上限。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A maximum total number of results to return from the query.\nIf negative, results are limited from the end of the query list towards the beginning.\nBy default, results are not limited.</p>\n\n</div>\n          \n          </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationOptions\n - api/animations/AnimationQueryMetadata\n - api/animations/query\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationOptions\n - api/animations/AnimationOptions#delay\n - api/animations/AnimationOptions#params\n - api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions#animationqueryoptions\n - api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions#instance-properties\n - api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions#limit\n - api/animations/AnimationQueryOptions#optional\n - api/animations/query\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts?message=docs(animations)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L577-L607\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L577-L607\n-->"}